Jason David Frank https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jason_David_Frank 0 Jason David Frank (born September 4, 1973) is an American actor, professional mixed martial artist, and former professional wrestler. He is most notable for his career as Tommy Oliver from the Power Rangers Franchise.
